Dear Cubic Frog® Users,
This app is a consolidation of our educational games. It replaces, but also contains EduKidsroom.
If you purchased the content of EduKidsRoom, it will automatically be unlocked in this app. If for any reason it’s locked, you can use the restore feature. 
The remaining Cubic Frog® educational games will be updated with information on how to restore them here. In the meantime, they can be used individually.
Please contact us at support@cubicfrog.com if you have any questions.
